The Spring Festival is approaching, and the Winter Olympics is around the corner. How is sustainable development being practiced at the Beijing Winter Olympics? How does the International Olympic Committee evaluate the preparation of the Beijing Winter Olympics? IOC Vice President Mr. Ng Ser Miang says that the Beijing 2022 organizing committee has committed a tremendous amount of resources and hard work to prepare for the Games. In February, Beijing will create Olympic history by becoming the first city to host both the Summer and Winter Olympic Games. There's no doubt that the Beijing 2022 Winter Olympic Games will be a resounding success and create its own unique legacies.